rows.label: qst702205_msg0001
rows.name:
I knew I dropped the key, sir,
but I was so busy running I
couldn't pick it up, sir.

rows.label: qst702205_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, but in a way, it's safe, sir!
It's deep inside the Grafton Feris
den in the Rakina Plains, sir.

rows.label: qst702205_msg0003
rows.name:
...I know, sir. I really
do regret this, sir.

rows.label: qst702205_msg0004
rows.name:
I just can't calm down
if I don't talk, sir...
